<div class="hgroup"><h1 class="title"><span class="title">更改在时钟中显示多少信息</span></h1></div>
<div class="region">
<div class="contents">
<p class="p">默认情况下，Ubuntu 仅在时钟中显示时间。您可以选择对时钟进行设置，以显示更多信息。</p>
<p class="p">点击时钟并选择<span class="gui">日期 &amp; 时间设置</span>。切换到 <span class="gui">时钟</span> 标签。选择您想要显示的时间和日期选项。</p>
<div class="note" title="备注"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><div class="contents">
<p class="p">您也可以通过取消选中<span class="gui">在菜单栏显示时钟</span>完全关闭时钟。</p>
<p class="p">If you later change your mind, you can get the clock back by clicking the
<span class="em">system menu</span> <span class="media"><span class="media media-image"><img src="figures/system-devices-panel.svg" class="media media-inline" alt="Power cog icon"></span></span> and selecting
<span class="gui">System Settings</span>. In the System section, click <span class="gui">Time &amp; Date</span>.
</p>
</div></div></div></div>
</div>
<div id="change-date-format" class="sect"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup"><h2 class="title"><span class="title">更改日期格式</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents">
<p class="p">您还可以更改时钟的日期格式以与您所在位置的首选标准一致。</p>
<div class="steps"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><ol class="steps">
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Click the <span class="em">system menu</span> <span class="media"><span class="media media-image"><img src="figures/system-devices-panel.svg" class="media media-inline" alt="Power cog icon"></span></span> and
    select <span class="gui">System Settings</span>.</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">在“个人”部分，单击<span class="gui">语言支持</span>。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">转到<span class="gui">区域格式</span>标签页。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">在下拉列表中选择您的首选位置。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">您需要 <span class="link"><a href="shell-exit.html" title="注销、关机、切换用户">注销</a></span>并重新登录此更改才会生效。</p></li>
</ol></div></div></div>
</div></div>
